title: LOVECRAFT COUNTRY Episode 8 Breakdown, New Theories, and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: 🎃💀Only 2 more episodes left of this great show! 💀🎃For all my Lovecraft videos check out my playlist: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k0J8wLNCR-4&list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7iHM0EeNo58UiU57xANu4S7&index=1&t=1s&ab_channel=ThinkStory
This episode was PURE JORDAN PEELE STYLE, The demon girls was creepy as hell but they was killing that choreo.
I think the curse prevents Dee from telling anybody about it, she tries to tell Letty about it and immediately starts choking, that's why she drew it.
symbolically I feel with those "demons" that follow Diana it represents how as African Americans we have negative stereotypes that follow us and haunt us relentlessly.
Shoutouts to the actors playing the demon sisters.
description:
In this video we take a deep dive, review, recap, and breakdown episode 8 "Jig-a-Bobo" of HBO's latest series Lovecraft Country based off the book by Matt Ruff. Review, recap, and easter eggs!
